          "plain_text": "Offering fast walls on larger sets and perfect walls on the insiders it can only be described as fun. Waves peel down the reef, bending slightly away from you - lending itself to a layback as the most functional form of burning speed back to the pocket of the wave. Usually no barrels on offer, but never say never. ",
