            "content": "We arrived there on the day of the biggest swell of our trip (and probably of the year), it was perfect. Double overhead and barrelling all the way, the swell had enough South in it to make the deathly end section makable. Sets come through when we’re on the boat and some of the best barrels that I’ve seen in my life are ridden to hoots from the channel. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "We arrived there on the day of the biggest swell of our trip (and probably of the year), it was perfect. Double overhead and barrelling all the way, the swell had enough South in it to make the deathly end section makable. Sets come through when we’re on the boat and some of the best barrels that I’ve seen in my life are ridden to hoots from the channel. ",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
    },
